The paper focuses on vulnerability assessment and static analysis of software code, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also discusses the implementation of the framework, which involves programming languages and compilers (cs.PL) and system analysis and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper uses machine learning techniques to improve the accuracy of the analysis, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG).
